{"tid":1676772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"商務部︰中美貿易協議文本技術性磋商基本完成","createTime":"2019-10-26T16:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T18:00:02.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4627ed91bf92bd3045f7bf1e87dc60358eafad40","tid":1676772,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"中美早前達成首階段貿易協議後，中國商務部確認，部分協議文本的技術性磋商基本完成。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表萊特希澤、財長努欽與副總理劉鶴周五通電話。中國商務部確認，雙方就美國進口中國熟禽肉、鯰魚產品的監管體系，以及中方解除美國禽肉對華出口禁令等達成共識，雙方牽頭人近期會再次通話。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表處就說，雙方在特定議題上取得進展，接近敲定首階段協議的部分內容。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488376-20191026.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488376-20191026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=66eb79c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488376-20191026.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6468adff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488376-20191026.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"321482db7274a2b82fa62698700536e8c0afe640","tid":1676772,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:13:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/pyCXhwYfV4Mfe/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FpyCXhwYfV4Mfe%2Fgiphy.gif&h=13215d7c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ce182023f0e6ba69347626291abe0c191418bd3","tid":1676772,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T16:14:06.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496c836e1aa576a9a0fb8bee660785dc255ebe1d","tid":1676772,"uid":130695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,